  "name": "Shared Nightmare",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>Merging minds with the target, you swap disorienting visions from one another's nightmares. One of you will become @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.yblD8fOR1J8rDwEQ]{Confused}, but which it'll be depends on the target's Will save.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Critical Success</strong> You are Confused for 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> At the start of your next turn, you spend your first action with the Confused condition, then act normally.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> As success, but the target is affected instead of you, spending its first action each turn Confused. The duration is 1 minute.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The target is Confused for 1 minute.</p>"
    },
